02:20:16,445 --> 02:20:18,276
You can see the wire

1274
02:20:19,085 --> 02:20:20,313
The charges

1275
02:22:23,365 --> 02:22:25,674
Don't wait for the train

1276
02:22:25,965 --> 02:22:27,000
Do it now

1277
02:22:53,445 --> 02:22:57,120
If Saito is correct  the train will arrive in 5 or 10 minutes

1278
02:22:57,365 --> 02:23:00,004
If you don't mind  I'll watch from up on the hill

1279
02:23:00,245 --> 02:23:02,076
Why  It's better from the bridge

1280
02:23:02,325 --> 02:23:05,681
It's hard to explain  sir  I'd rather not be a part of it

1281
02:23:05,925 --> 02:23:10,077
As you please  Honestly  sometimes I don't understand you at all

1282
02:23:10,325 --> 02:23:14,477
As you once said  sir  I've got a lot to learn about the army

1283
02:23:21,165 --> 02:23:22,484
Good morning

1284
