River's gone down in the night

1285
02:25:05,325 --> 02:25:06,440
What's he doing

1286
02:25:51,325 --> 02:25:54,317
Colonel  there's something rather odd going on

1287
02:25:54,565 --> 02:25:58,080
I think we better have a look around before that train comes across

1288
02:26:54,525 --> 02:26:55,878
He's gone mad

1289
