02:28:43,685 --> 02:28:47,473
Have you a knife  I just realized the bridge has been mined

1294
02:28:47,685 --> 02:28:49,045
Mined

1295
02:28:55,685 --> 02:28:56,720
Good boy

1296
02:29:01,485 --> 02:29:04,124
British officer Here to blow up the bridge

1297
02:29:04,365 --> 02:29:08,324
Blow up the bridge  Yes  sir  British commando orders

1298
02:29:08,565 --> 02:29:11,079
Blow up the bridge   Yes  There's no time

1299
02:29:11,285 --> 02:29:13,640
No  no Help

1300
02:29:20,605 --> 02:29:22,800
Kill him Kill him

1301
02:29:23,165 --> 02:29:25,520
Let me go  sir You don't understand

1302
02:29:26,525 --> 02:29:29,278
Kill him Kill him

1303
02:29:39,165 --> 02:29:40,883
Kill him  Joyce

1304
02:30:32,165 --> 02:30:33,154
You

1305
02:30:34,125 --> 02:30:35,717
You

1306
02:30:49,045 --> 02:30:50,717
What have I done

1307
02:31:56,605 --> 02:31:58,084
Madness

1308
